<div class='flex flex-col space-y-8'>
  <section class='space-y-8 text-center'>
    <h1 class="font-bold text-4xl">🪄 One click blog from your Instagram.</h1>

    <div>
      <% unless current_user %>
        <%= link_to '🎯 Connect your Instagram', instagram_authorize_path, class: 'bg-violet-700 hover:bg-violet-900 text-fuchsia-50 p-4 rounded-md font-bold' %>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <div>
      <%= link_to '👀 See examples', insta_users_path, class: 'bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-900 text-fuchsia-50 p-4 rounded-md' %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class='space-y-4'>
    <h2 class='font-bold text-3xl text-center'>🧐 How it works</h2>
    <div class="list-decimal">
      <div>
        🔑 1. Connect your Instagram account to Insta2Blog
      </div>
      <div>
        ✍️ 2. Post on Instagram, as usual
      </div>
      <div>
        🧘‍♀️ 3. Relax
      </div>
    </div> 

    <div>
      Every time you post on Instagram, we will 🪄🦄 automagically create a blog post on your insta2blog website.
    </div>

    <div>
      For example, if your account on instagram is <b><%= @random_user.username %></b>, your blog posts will be at <b><%= link_to insta_user_posts_url(@random_user), @random_user, target: '_blank', rel: 'noopener' %></b>.
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class='space-y-4'>
    <h2 class='font-bold text-3xl text-center'>⁉️ What for?</h2>
    <div>
      <div>
        🧘‍♀️ Run a blog without the tension of maintaining a blog.
      </div>

      <div>
        🥇 Boost your SEO ranking. Instagram posts do not rank in Google. Yours will
      </div>

      <div>
        🧐 Own the experience on your blog. Don't compete for attention with other creators on Instagram.
      </div>

      <div>
        🔍 Quick search for posts on your profile.
      </div>

      <div>
        #️⃣ Hashtag search only for YOUR content. Don't redirect traffic out of your blog!
      </div>

      <div>
        🔗 Anybody can link to your content. Avoid the instagram registration wall.
      </div>

      <div>
        ♻️ Make your content "evergreen". Give a second life to old posts by making them more accessible. 
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <%# <h2 class='font-bold text-3xl text-center'>📧 Get notified about the launch 🚀</h2> %>
</div>
